::CyberShark::

    He got the message from Pantron. He really didn't want to leave Battera, 
but knowing where Pantron was he didn't want to bring her either.
    "Battera, if you wish you can return to my base and hang out untill I 
return. I have to go to Hell Beast's layer to retrive a fallen comrade. I 
will be back." CyberShark called out ot Battera.
    He zommed away toward Hell Beast's base. As soon as he was in radar range 
he cloaked. He went in and fired everything he had at Sniper. He knew it 
proboly wouldn't kill him, but it would make him think about attacking the 
Destrons again. He landed and picked up Pantron. He then lifted off and flew 
off to the Destron base.
